{"tid":2178534,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"葉劉: 點樣先可以令黑社會都做全民檢測? 張建宗: 要求從事「地下活動」嘅人做檢測係好困難","createTime":"2020-08-28T12:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T13:37:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8fec55f264e3e44f7c90aaf658a35dbad6223fec","tid":2178534,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T12:24:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/2YG7TPQBXFHOXDNPBHKPERHJNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2F2YG7TPQBXFHOXDNPBHKPERHJNM%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=4ed9540f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2F2YG7TPQBXFHOXDNPBHKPERHJNM%2F&h=16f0e1e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/2YG7TPQBXFHOXDNPBHKPERHJNM/</a><br />\n<br />\n做過保安局局長嘅新民黨葉劉淑儀，今日（28日）就喺內會質疑「黑社會係隱形帶菌者」，事關佢哋成日進行「地下活動」，仲要求政府解釋，點樣先可以令黑社會都做全民檢測。<br />\n<br />\n出席內會嘅政務司司長張建宗又係用返嗰招：動以之情。佢承認要求從事「地下活動」嘅人做檢測係好困難，但就話病毒好「狡猾」，「無論咩背景嘅人都有家人，點解唔保護佢呢？」葉劉唔多滿意張建宗嘅回應，話黑社會唔係「善良市民」，擔心非法地下活動會有隱形傳播，要求警方要多加行動。"},{"pid":"a5df6a75b4824c06e04fca94d90dd16e6634de07","tid":2178534,"uid":231583,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T12:26:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f9802b07576fc6134a9f75a4df427870ee0dc88","tid":2178534,"uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T12:26:52.000Z","msg":"3萬黨員只有一個唔報到，憑咩要求市民報到 ?"},{"pid":"3724462ed9a56c9725fa390b3f4e8a96f3842d22","tid":2178534,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T12:27:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac3ea35bb04a4598e644a21d3850cdd4a1373362","tid":2178534,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"黑社會⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p